---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Productivity Hacks">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header class="page-header" id="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>
        <span class="gradient-text">Privacy</span> Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">
        Your privacy matters to us. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
  <section class="legal-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">
        <p class="legal-date">Effective Date: March 14, 2026</p>

        <p>
          At Productivity Hacks, we recognize that the privacy of your personal information is important. This policy
          outlines the types of information we receive and collect when you use our site and how we safeguard your
          information.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p>
          We do not require any user registration or personal data (such as names or email addresses) to access our free
          productivity guide. Our goal is to provide a friction-free experience for our visitors.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Log Files and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          Like most other websites, we collect and use the data contained in log files. The information in the log files
          includes your IP address, your ISP, the browser you used to visit our site, the time you visited our site, and
          which pages you visited throughout our site. This is used solely for analyzing trends and improving the site
          experience.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Cookies and Web Beacons</h2>
        <p>
          We do use cookies to store information, such as your personal preferences when you visit our site.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Advertising and Monetization</h2>
        <p>
          We use Monetag as a third-party advertising provider. Monetag may use cookies and web beacons in the course of
          ads being served on our website. These cookies allow the ad network to serve ads to you based on your visit to
          this site and other sites on the Internet.
        </p>
        <p>
          Productivity Hacks has no access to or control over these cookies that are used by third-party advertisers.
          You should consult the respective Privacy Policies of these third-party ad servers for more detailed
          information on their practices.
        </p>

        <h2>5. External Links and Downloads</h2>
        <p>
          Our site contains links to external file-hosting services (such as Google Drive) to deliver our free ebook. We
          are not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of such external websites.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Consent</h2>
        <p>
          By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its Terms and Conditions.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please visit our <a href="/contact" >Contact
            page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  
</Layout>
